        "subject": "LU-4591 osc: allow lock to be cancelled at ENQ time",
        "message": "LU-4591 osc: allow lock to be cancelled at ENQ time\n\nIt's a rewrite of git commit 13079de3417ce41ce485b2bdad36834e2f6e6e15\n\nInstead of preventing unusing a CLS_ENQUEUED cl_lock, add error\nhandling of CLS_NEW cl_lock in osc_lock_upcall().\n\nSigned-off-by: Bobi Jam <bobijam.xu@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Ia946746a083f449b71eceac7fd6b8614ea87b689\n"
      },
